OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering a
OL,4,CScottish Borders woman
OL,6,FA 31-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto murdering a woman from Duns.
OL,9,FCorey Dryden will appear for
OL,10,Fsentencing at the High Court in
OL,11,FEdinburgh on 24 July 2025 after
OL,12,Fpleading guilty to murder today.
OL,14,FPolice Scotland were called to reports
OL,15,Fof serious injury to Megan Hughes, 31,
OL,16,Fat a property on Windram Road, in
OL,17,FChirnside, near Duns, on 9 February
OL,18,F2025.
