OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to murdering a
OL,4,CScottish Borders woman
OL,6,FEmergency services pronounced the 31-
OL,7,Fyear-old woman dead at the scene.
OL,8,FDryden was later charged in connection
OL,9,Fwith her death after being arrested on
OL,10,Fthe same day.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Laura White
OL,13,Fsaid: "This was a vicious and
OL,14,Fcalculated attack by Dryden that
OL,15,Ftragically resulted in Megan's death.
OL,16,FHis actions have robbed a family of
OL,17,Ftheir mum, daughter, granddaughter,
OL,18,Fsister and niece.
